00:30:51,049 --> 00:30:53,108
Yeah. She looks good.
She's a little feisty.

544
00:30:53,184 --> 00:30:54,913
My mom?
You gotta be kidding me.

545
00:30:54,986 --> 00:30:56,851
You ready to see her, Dad?

546
00:30:56,988 --> 00:30:58,853
Oh, wait a second, Dad.
Let me...

