00:38:59,804 --> 00:39:00,964
Yes, sir. Here. Right here.

744
00:39:01,038 --> 00:39:02,471
Actually, he's Jake Tremont.

745
00:39:02,540 --> 00:39:04,007
I'm his son, John.

746
00:39:04,075 --> 00:39:05,667
You probably don't
need to know that,

747
00:39:05,743 --> 00:39:07,608
but now you do anyway.

748
00:39:17,088 --> 00:39:19,488
You can't sit there
during the test, sir.

749
00:39:19,557 --> 00:39:21,149
Oh, I'm sorry.

750
00:39:28,766 --> 00:39:30,393
Uh, you can't be
in the car at all.

751
00:39:30,468 --> 00:39:31,560
What are you talking about?

752
00:39:31,635 --> 00:39:32,727
This is my father.

753
00:39:32,803 --> 00:39:34,065
It's against the law.

754
00:39:34,138 --> 00:39:36,732
I won't say a word.
You won't even know I'm here.

755
00:39:36,807 --> 00:39:39,241
I can't administer the test
with you in the car.

756
00:39:39,310 --> 00:39:40,834
Either you get out now,

757
00:39:40,911 --> 00:39:43,402
or your father
gets a failing grade.

758
00:39:45,683 --> 00:39:46,945
You going to be okay?

759
00:39:47,017 --> 00:39:49,144
I will be
as soon as you go.

