00:42:13,130 --> 00:42:14,893
at the American Express office
in Tecoman

779
00:42:14,965 --> 00:42:16,398
and I got a letter
from Aunt Annie.

780
00:42:16,467 --> 00:42:17,866
Told me that
Grandma was sick.

781
00:42:17,935 --> 00:42:19,232
So I hustled back.

782
00:42:19,303 --> 00:42:21,168
I figured you might need
some help, Grandpa.

783
00:42:21,238 --> 00:42:22,830
Never mind
helping your Grandpa.

784
00:42:22,907 --> 00:42:24,636
When was
the last time you ate?

